{"tid":2314314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国火箭升空  雲南多個鄉鎮緊急疏散防衛星殘骸墜落","createTime":"2020-12-06T12:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T01:12:18.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f201e08041de76553bbf004d6111c6311fd5f4f","tid":2314314,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"中國對航天工業缺乏信心？官媒新華社今天（6日）報導，當局在11時58分於四川西昌衛星發射中心，利用長征三號乙運載火箭，發射高分十四號升空，當局宣稱發射成功，衛星進入預定軌道，可是雲南省西雙版納卻發出緊急通告，要求多個鄉鎮民眾疏散，以防止有火箭殘骸墜落，更嚴禁擅自拍照、錄影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201206/GCHUHF6WFJGNLEMX3TTY3QY4KE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201206%2FGCHUHF6WFJGNLEMX3TTY3QY4KE%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2v1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=d47a68ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201206%2FGCHUHF6WFJGNLEMX3TTY3QY4KE%2F&h=941c9a52\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201206/GCHUHF6WFJGNLEMX3TTY3QY4KE/</a>"},{"pid":"ebbb480fc4fae16328ad9fa74aafc40a276cbad8","tid":2314314,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be1c28019bf8c3b7a16b0a816cb78139863b82b","tid":2314314,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de96b0a2e5047ec42b748fa05886cb10ec7fc70","tid":2314314,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e388de6ef59ff2a776ac5f10f88c551b332905"